\subsection{Method \code{get_transferable()}}{
Get Transferable Balance

Retrieves the amount of a currency that is available for transfer out of a
specific account type. Use this before calling \code{add_transfer()} to verify
sufficient funds are available.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated GET with \code{currency} and \code{type} (required) and optional \code{tag} query parameters.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Returns a \code{data.table} with balance breakdown.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/accounts/transferable}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/account-info/transfer/get-transfer-quotas}{KuCoin Get Transfer Quotas}

Verified: 2026-05-23
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Pre-Flight Check}: Verify \code{transferable} amount before initiating a transfer.
\item \strong{Balance Awareness}: Monitor \code{holds} to understand how much is locked in open orders.
\item \strong{Fund Routing}: Check transferable amounts across account types to optimise fund allocation.
}
}

